“DAILY EXPESNE TRACKER SYSTEM”

=>Introduction:
Daily Expense Tracker System is designed to keep a track of Income-Expense
an organisation on a day-to-day basis. This System divides the Income based
On Daily Expenses. If exceed day’s expense, system will calculate income and
will provide new daily expense allowed amount.
Daily expense tracking System will generate report at the end of And
employees send reports Like On (Pdf,Print).
In this application, user can provide his income to calculate his total
expenses per day and these results will be stored for each user.
The application has the provision to predict the income and expense for the
manager using data mining.
The expense tracker will help any organization to deal with all their
expenses more efficiently. By using software for managing tracking
will help to control unnecessary expenses.



How to run the Daily Expense Tracking System  Project
1. Download the  zip file
2. Extract the file and copy dets folder
3.Paste inside root directory(for xampp xampp/htdocs, for wamp wamp/www, for lamp var/www/html)
4. Open PHPMyAdmin (http://localhost/phpmyadmin)
5. Create a database with name dets_db
6. Import dets_db.sql file(given inside the zip package in sql file folder)
7.Run the script http://localhost/Daily_Expense_Tracker_Project(frontend)



